# A screen-based TERMINFO that adds the escape sequences for italic,
# and overwrites conflicting sequences for standout text.
#
# Based on:
#
#   https://gist.github.com/sos4nt/3187620
#
# Install:
#
#   mkdir ~/.terminfo # otpional; can also install to $HOME/share/terminfo
#   tic screen-italic.terminfo
#
# Usage:
#
#   export TERM=screen-italic
#
screen-italic|screen with italic,
  sitm=\E[3m, ritm=\E[23m,
  smso=\E[7m, rmso=\E[27m,
  use=screen,
